kgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不如講白d實際執行指令嘅係中聯辦啦"},{"pid":"9c0a6a6d6f113711cbf1fc6e04724ac6b0ef63e2","tid":1912533,"uid":34553,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T07:05:22.000Z","msg":"又借啲意屌鳩妹妹唔聽人意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97cc9be2d497c6fd257e37420e67d174c2092d35","tid":1912533,"uid":111316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T07:06:33.000Z","msg":"又黎狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n召喚閉門會議高官互毆潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c0ce8df096e6f06f6b79b37b6cdd7dc7c7b4c9f","tid":1912533,"uid":70336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T07:40:18.000Z","msg":"割到爛"}]}